Summary: Looked out of window saw a small cylinder object come toward me, it was rotating and moving fast.
divs: Sighting Detailslooked out of back window, I saw a cylinder object come rooftop toward me. it was rotating fast, orange and yellow top, with a red bottom. it was coming toward me, then it stopped and turned to my right went behind trees, and moved up. I knew that it wasn't over. I went to the kitchen, and noticed that 2 more minutes had passed. I was having a head ache. I went back to the window. I noticed a white light in the same direction,and then it moved above the trees to my left.
